  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.esoco.lib.event.Event<java.util.Map<K,V>>

    public class MapEvent<K,V>
extends de.esoco.lib.event.ElementEvent<java.util.Map<K,V>,K,V>
    An element event subclass that contains informations related to map modifications. The element value of a map event always describes the map key that is affected by the event while the update value contains the map value for this key.
